</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-177_">Evidence of Making Safeguarding Personal in practice
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-179_">Governance and audit trails showing learning from incidents.

</li></ul><p class="sc-hGMjVM kxdODp pf-181_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-b7881c92-e3f9-4589-8275-1a9b0fabfbbb"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content "><strong>Provider insight</strong> - Failing to embed safeguarding not only risks harm. It results in Inadequate ratings, enforcement action, and reputational damage.
